snippet.title: SOS Closed Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.sosgame.com
SOS is an interactive gameshow where the world’s most entertaining performers scheme for their survival on La Cuna Island. Players must find a relic, signal for extraction, and grab one of three spots on the rescue chopper. Survivors will be rewarded with fame and fortune, not to mention their lives.

Beta runs December 11-17.
